snippet.title: The Witch and the Hundred Knight 2 - Gameplay Trailer (PS4)
snippet.description:
Pre-order today @ http://bit.ly/Witch100Knight2
Learn more @ http://WitchHundred2.com

The Hundred Knight has a lot to overcome as it helps Amalie and Chelka in The Witch and the Hundred Knight 2. Witness Mystical Dodge, Depletura, and other skills that will help Hundred Knight defeat foes and survive in Kevala!

Keep up with all of the latest info by following us on Facebook (/NISAmericaInc) and on Twitter (@NISAmerica). Visit http://nisamerica.com/ to learn more.
